tags.name: Stringers Ridge West Bell Avenue Trailhead

tags.inscription: To the east, at the mouth of Chattanooga Creek, was this supply base for Tennessee troops during the Creek War of 1812-13. The river here forms Moccasin Bend in its efforts to break through the mountains.
